        "service_requests"
      ],
      "consumers": [],
      "description": "Employee self-service intake surface: catalog browse, request submission, knowledge search, and case status. Workflow layer on top of HRSD-CASE-MGMT, no masters of its own. Hands intake off to case-mgmt and can route IT-flavored requests through to ITSM."
    },
